    <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d752.3728410130734!2d28.978542829250976!3d41.03638261029184!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14cab766d0fddca1%3A0xa77f81fb558f5ce3!2sTaksim%20360!5e0!3m2!1sen!2str!4v1629459462726!5m2!1sen!2str" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" aria-hidden="false" tabindex="0"></iframe>
</div>